data.description: Welcome to this beautifully renovated 3bed / 2bath single family home in Moravia Walther. The main floor of the home offers an open floor plan with a cozy family room and separate dining area. The well-kept kitchen has beautiful wood cabinetry with ample storage and counter space. You will also find all three bedrooms and one of the full baths on the main level. The basement is finished and has an additional full bathroom. The property features sizable front and back yards, and there is room for two cars in the driveway. The roof, in addition to the entire HVAC system and hot water heater, have all been recently replaced.
